{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Coordinates","mdn_url":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/GeolocationCoordinates","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Geolocation_API\">Geolocation API</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/GeolocationCoordinates\"><code>GeolocationCoordinates</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Propriedades</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/GeolocationCoordinates/accuracy\"><code>accuracy</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/GeolocationCoordinates/altitude\"><code>altitude</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/GeolocationCoordinates/altitudeAccuracy\"><code>altitudeAccuracy</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/GeolocationCoordinates/heading\"><code>heading</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/GeolocationCoordinates/latitude\"><code>latitude</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/GeolocationCoordinates/longitude\"><code>longitude</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/GeolocationCoordinates/speed\"><code>speed</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Páginas relacionadas a Geolocation API</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Geolocation\"><code>Geolocation</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/GeolocationPosition\"><code>GeolocationPosition</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/GeolocationPositionError\"><code>GeolocationPositionError</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Navigator/geolocation\"><code>Navigator.geolocation</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"propriedades","title":"<font><font>Propriedades</font></font>","isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\">\n<div id=\"sect2\"><div class=\"notecard secure\" id=\"sect3\"><p><strong>Secure context:</strong> This feature is available only in <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Security/Secure_Contexts\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">secure contexts (en-US)</a> (HTTPS), in some or all <a href=\"#browser_compatibility\">supporting browsers</a>.</p></div></div>\n\n<p>O&nbsp;<strong><code>Coordinates</code></strong> iinterface representa a posição e a altitude do dispositivo na Terra,&nbsp;bem como a precisão com que essas propriedades são calculadas.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><em>A interface do&nbsp;<code>Coordinates</code>&nbsp;não herda nenhuma propiedade</em>.</p>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"coordinates.latitude_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/GeolocationCoordinates/latitude\"><code>Coordinates.latitude</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <span title=\"Este valor não pode ser alterado.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Somente leitura </span> <span class=\"notecard inline secure\" title=\"This feature is available only in secure contexts (HTTPS)\">Secure context</span></dt>\n <dd>Retorna&nbsp;um&nbsp;<code>double</code> representando a latitude da posição em graus decimais.</dd>\n <dt id=\"coordinates.longitude_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/GeolocationCoordinates/longitude\"><code>Coordinates.longitude</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <span title=\"Este valor não pode ser alterado.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Somente leitura </span> <span class=\"notecard inline secure\" title=\"This feature is available only in secure contexts (HTTPS)\">Secure context</span></dt>\n <dd>Retorna um&nbsp;<code>double</code> representando a longitude da posição em graus decimais.</dd>\n <dt id=\"coordinates.altitude\"><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/GeolocationCoordinates/altitude\"><code>Coordinates.altitude</code></a> <span title=\"Este valor não pode ser alterado.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Somente leitura </span> <span class=\"notecard inline secure\" title=\"This feature is available only in secure contexts (HTTPS)\">Secure context</span></dt>\n <dd>Retorna um&nbsp;<code>double</code> <font>representando a altitude da posição em metros, em relação ao nível do mar.&nbsp;</font><font>Esse valor pode ser</font> <code>null</code>&nbsp;se a implementação não puder fornecer os dados.</dd>\n <dt id=\"coordinates.accuracy_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/GeolocationCoordinates/accuracy\"><code>Coordinates.accuracy</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <span title=\"Este valor não pode ser alterado.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Somente leitura </span> <span class=\"notecard inline secure\" title=\"This feature is available only in secure contexts (HTTPS)\">Secure context</span></dt>\n <dd>Retorna&nbsp;um&nbsp;<code>double</code> <font>representação da precisão das&nbsp;</font><font>propriedades em</font> <code>latitude</code>&nbsp;e&nbsp;<code>longitude</code>, expressa em metros.</dd>\n <dt id=\"coordinates.altitudeaccuracy_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/GeolocationCoordinates/altitudeAccuracy\"><code>Coordinates.altitudeAccuracy</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <span title=\"Este valor não pode ser alterado.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Somente leitura </span> <span class=\"notecard inline secure\" title=\"This feature is available only in secure contexts (HTTPS)\">Secure context</span></dt>\n <dd>Retorna&nbsp;um <code>double</code> representação da precisão da&nbsp;<code>altitude</code> expressa&nbsp;em metros. Esse valor pode ser <code>null</code>.</dd>\n <dt id=\"coordinates.heading_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/GeolocationCoordinates/heading\"><code>Coordinates.heading</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <span title=\"Este valor não pode ser alterado.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Somente leitura </span> <span class=\"notecard inline secure\" title=\"This feature is available only in secure contexts (HTTPS)\">Secure context</span></dt>\n <dd>Retorna um&nbsp;<code>double</code><font><font>&nbsp;representação da direção na qual o dispositivo está viajando.&nbsp;</font><font>Esse valor, especificado em graus, indica o quão longe do título verdadeiro do norte do dispositivo.&nbsp;</font></font><code>0</code> <font><font>representam o verdadeiro norte e a direção é determinada no sentido horário (o que significa que o leste é&nbsp;</font></font><code>90</code><font><font>graus e oeste é&nbsp;</font></font><code>270</code><font><font>graus).&nbsp;</font><font>Se&nbsp;</font></font><code>speed</code><font><font>é&nbsp;</font></font><code>0</code><font><font>,&nbsp;</font></font><code>heading</code><font><font>é&nbsp;</font></font><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/NaN\" title=\"/en-US/docs/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/NaN\">NaN</a></code><font><font>.&nbsp;</font><font>Se o dispositivo não conseguir fornecer&nbsp;</font></font><code>heading</code><font><font>informações, esse valor é&nbsp;</font></font><code>null</code><font><font>.</font></font></dd>\n <dt id=\"coordinates.speed_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/GeolocationCoordinates/speed\"><code>Coordinates.speed</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <span title=\"Este valor não pode ser alterado.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Somente leitura </span> <span class=\"notecard inline secure\" title=\"This feature is available only in secure contexts (HTTPS)\">Secure context</span></dt>\n <dd><font><font>Retorna um&nbsp;</font></font><code>double</code><font><font>representação da velocidade do dispositivo em metros por segundo.&nbsp;</font><font>Esse valor pode ser&nbsp;</font></font><code>null</code><font><font>.</font></font></dd>\n</dl>\n\n<h2 id=\"métodos\"><font><font>Métodos</font></font></h2>\n\n<p><em><em><font><font>A&nbsp;interface da&nbsp;</font></font><code>Coordinates</code><font><font>&nbsp;</font></font><em><font><font>não implementa, nem herda nenhum método.</font></font></em></em></em></p>\n\n<h2 id=\"specifications\">Specifications</h2>\n\n<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Specification</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comment</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/geolocation-api/#coordinates\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Geolocation API<br><small lang=\"pt-BR\">The definition of 'Coordinates' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Recomendação</span></td>\n   <td>Especificação inicial.</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n\n<h2 id=\"browser_compatibility\">Compatibilidade com navegadores</h2>\n\n<p></p><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect4\"><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Estamos convertendo nossos dados de compatibilidade para o formato JSON</a></strong>.\n            Esta tabela de compatibilidade ainda usa o formato antigo,\n            pois ainda não convertemos os dados que ela contém.\n            <strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Structures/Compatibility_tables\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Descubra como você pode ajudar! (en-US)</a></strong></div>\n\n<div class=\"htab\" id=\"sect5\">\n    <a id=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\" name=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\"></a>\n    <ul>\n        <li class=\"selected\"><a href=\"#compat-desktop\">Desktop</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"#compat-mobile\">Dispositivo móvel</a></li>\n    </ul>\n</div><p></p>\n\n<div id=\"compat-desktop\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Característica</th>\n   <th>Chrome</th>\n   <th>Edge</th>\n   <th>Firefox (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>Internet Explorer</th>\n   <th>Opera</th>\n   <th>Safari</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Suporte básico</td>\n   <td>5</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/3.5\" title=\"Released on 2009-06-30.\">3.5</a> (1.9.1)</td>\n   <td>9</td>\n   <td>10.60<br>\n    Removed in 15.0<br>\n    Reintroduced in 16.0</td>\n   <td>5</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Apenas contexto seguro</td>\n   <td>47</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/55\" title=\"Released on 2017-08-08.\">55</a> (55)</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-mobile\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Característica</th>\n   <th>Android</th>\n   <th>Chrome for Android</th>\n   <th>Edge</th>\n   <th>Firefox Mobile (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>IE Mobile</th>\n   <th>Opera Mobile</th>\n   <th>Safari Mobile</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Suporte básico</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td>4.0 (4)</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td>10.60</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Apenas contexto seguro</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td>47</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/55\" title=\"Released on 2017-08-08.\">55</a> (55)</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<h2 id=\"veja_também\">Veja também</h2>\n\n<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Geolocation\" title=\"/ en-US / docs / WebAPI / Using_geolocation\"><font><font>Usando geolocalização</font></font></a></li>\n <li>O <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Geolocation\"><code>Geolocation</code></a>&nbsp; e a&nbsp;&nbsp;interface que o usa.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<ul>\n</ul>","titleAsText":"Propriedades"}}],"toc":[{"text":"<font><font>Propriedades</font></font>","id":"propriedades"}],"summary":"O Coordinates iinterface representa a posição e a altitude do dispositivo na Terra, bem como a precisão com que essas propriedades são calculadas.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"GeolocationCoordinates","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Coordinates","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Coordinates","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"GeolocationCoordinates","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Coordinates","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"Coordinates","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"},{"title":"Coordinates","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"pt-br/web/api/geolocationcoordinates","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pt-br/web/api/geolocationcoordinates/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web","title":"Tecnologia Web para desenvolvedores"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API","title":"APIs da Web"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/GeolocationCoordinates","title":"Coordinates"}],"pageTitle":"Coordinates - APIs da Web | MDN","noIndexing":false}}